#Decision tree
library(rpart)

predict_decisiontrees <- predict(decision_trees_mm, newdata = test_set, type = c("class"))
mm_DecisionTree <- confusionMatrix(data = as.factor(predict_decisiontrees), reference = as.factor(test_set$y), positive = "no")
